OL,3,CScottish greyhound racing ban would be
OL,4,C'silly', says trainer
OL,6,FA greyhound trainer from Cumbria has
OL,7,Fsaid plans to ban greyhound racing in
OL,8,FScotland would be "silly" after all
OL,9,Fthe country's racing tracks have now
OL,10,Fclosed.
OL,12,FIt comes as MSPs vote on whether to
OL,13,Fprogress a bill to ban racing in
OL,14,FScotland.
OL,16,FGreen MSP Mark Ruskell has piloted the
OL,17,Flegislation and said it would put an
OL,18,Fend to a "cruel industry."
