OL,3,CScottish greyhound racing ban would be
OL,4,C'silly', says trainer
OL,6,FHe said: "I think there's every chance
OL,7,Fif this bill doesn't pass, greyhound
OL,8,Fracing will come back in Scotland.
OL,10,F"It's inherently dangerous and I don't
OL,11,Fthink it has a place in our modern
OL,12,Fsociety, we need to bring this
OL,13,Fsuffering to an end."
OL,15,FLifelong Cumbrian greyhound trainer
OL,16,FJoe Edgar, along with the Greyhound
OL,17,FBoard of Great Britain, insists the
OL,18,Fsport is safe.
