OL,3,CScottish greyhound racing ban would be
OL,4,C'silly', says trainer
OL,6,FMr Edgar said: "It's something I've
OL,7,Fdone all my life, we used to have a
OL,8,Ftrack in Workington when I was young.
OL,10,F"You go back to the days of the mining
OL,11,Ftowns when there was not a lot else to
OL,12,Fdo on a Saturday, everyone went to the
OL,13,Fdogs.
OL,15,F"Welfare is really really important,
OL,16,Fwe have to do the best by our dogs, we
OL,17,Fhave inspections all the time, the
OL,18,Fdogs are well cared for.
