OL,3,CScottish greyhound racing ban would be
OL,4,C'silly', says trainer
OL,6,F"It seems a bit silly to me really,
OL,7,Fthere's no tracks left in Scotland so
OL,8,Fwhat they're trying to ban doesn't
OL,9,Factually happen anyway."
OL,11,FIn 2024 greyhound racing in Scotland
OL,12,Fstopped altogether when Thorton
OL,13,FStadium in Fife closed its doors.
OL,15,FWhile the bill goes through the
OL,16,FScottish Parliament, there are
OL,17,Fcurrently no plans for a similar ban
OL,18,Fin England.
