OL,3,CScottish greyhound racing ban would be
OL,4,C'silly', says trainer
OL,6,FAnimal rights campaigner Eve Massie
OL,7,FBishop said: "Greyhound racing is
OL,8,Finherently harmful and that is because
OL,9,Fof the inherent risks when they're
OL,10,Fforced to run at high speeds around an
OL,11,Foval track, when there's a high risk
OL,12,Fof injury, and sadly, greyhounds
OL,13,Fdying."
OL,15,FThe Greyhound Board of Great Britain
OL,16,Fsaid:
OL,18,F"This is a vanity Bill attempting to
OL,19,Fban something which doesn't currently
OL,20,Ftake place.
